Yeah.

00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:04.900
My name?

00:06:05.060 --> 00:06:06.180
Kar-Lai

00:06:06.560 --> 00:06:08.480
And he don't have English name.

00:06:08.980 --> 00:06:10.900
Gé Yôu Yuán, his Chinese name.

